   arm_instr (a, i: word32) =
   { (arm_c_MEM a, arm_d_word8 ((7 >< 0) i));
     (arm_c_MEM (a + 1w), arm_d_word8 ((15 >< 8) i));
     (arm_c_MEM (a + 2w), arm_d_word8 ((23 >< 16) i));
     (arm_c_MEM (a + 3w), arm_d_word8 ((31 >< 24) i)) }`

